Output ../gifs/rcc-audit.gif
Set Theme "Ayu Mirage"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 800
Set Height 600
Set Padding 32
Set Framerate 12
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.5
Hide
Type "cd $HOME/Raccoon" Enter
Type "alias rcc=$HOME/Raccoon/docs/gif-helpers/demo-audit.sh" Enter
Show

Type "rcc --deep --dry-run" Sleep 400ms Enter
Sleep 6s
ScrollDown 5
Sleep 2s
